data.description: END UNIT!!!  ASK ME HOW TO DROP YOUR INTEREST RATE BY 2 PERCENT!!  Welcome to your new home in beautiful Villa Medici!  This charming townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience! With three bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms there is plenty of space for your family or guest!  Upstairs, you'll find the well-appointed bedrooms, each offering laminate wood flooring and plenty of space. This townhome is located only 12-15 minutes from Fort Myers Beach!!  Plus, you are just a short drive away, seven minutes, from the Lakes Park which holds farmers market yoga and other fun events for the family! This unit features a 2 car garage with the master on the first floor plus a brand new chair lift for the stairs was installed just a year ago in this unit! Don't miss this opportunity to live out your dream in southwest Florida it this fantastic townhome! Contact me today to schedule a viewing!!
